# 🏠 Home Page — Pinterest-Style Masonry

Inspired by **Pinterest's homepage**. Dense visual discovery grid. Each card = one tool/experiment.

## 🎯 Vibe in One Line

> Warm, cozy, image-first masonry grid. Browse your tools like browsing a Pinterest board.

## 🎨 Palette

| Role | Color | Notes |
|------|-------|-------|
| Page background | `#F5F0E8` (warm cream) | NOT white — warm and cozy like Pinterest's sand tones |
| Card background | `#FFFFFF` | Clean white cards on cream |
| Brand accent | `#DC143C` (crimson) | Logo, FAB, primary CTAs only — bold and singular |
| Primary text | `#1A1A1A` | Card titles |
| Secondary text | `rgba(0,0,0,0.5)` | Descriptions |
| Metadata text | `rgba(0,0,0,0.4)` | Labels, timestamps |
| Status: live | `#22C55E` | Green dot |
| Status: building | `#DC143C` | Crimson dot |
| Hover shadow | `0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` | Subtle lift on hover |

## 📐 Layout — Masonry Grid

- **Masonry grid** for experiment/tool cards (Pinterest's signature layout)
- Columns: `5+ → 3 → 2 → 1` as viewport shrinks
- Cards have **varying heights** — no uniform rows
- Tight gap between cards (8-12px) — content density IS the value
- No heavy shadows on cards — content carries the visual weight
- Generous border-radius: **16px** on cards, **20px+** on large containers

## 🔤 Typography

| Element | Font | Size | Weight | Style |
|---------|------|------|--------|-------|
| Page title "SAVY" | Playfair Display | clamp(42px, 8vw, 58px) | 400 | italic |
| Card title | Playfair Display | 22px | 400 | normal |
| Card description | Inter | 14px | 400 | normal |
| Section header | Inter | 15px | 800 | uppercase, tracked |
| Label / metadata | Inter | 11px | 600 | uppercase, 0.12em tracking |

