## 🔘 FAB (Floating Action Button)

- Position: fixed bottom-right (24px offset)
- Size: 56px circle
- Background: crimson `#DC143C`
- Shadow: `0 4px 16px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.3)`
- Icon: white "+" at 28px

## ✅ Do

- Use masonry grid layout — cards stack like Pinterest pins
- Keep cards tight — density = discovery
- Warm cream background, never cold gray or pure white page
- Border-radius 12-16px on cards — generous, rounded, cozy
- Photography/visuals in cards when possible — image-first

## 🚫 Don't

- Don't use the nutrition palette (yellow/ocean/magenta) on this page
- Don't use heavy shadows — Pinterest is flat, depth comes from content
- Don't make all cards the same height — varied heights = visual interest
- Don't use small border-radius (<12px) — generous rounding is core
- Don't add the SavySiteHeader to home — home has no header bar
